Liese: "This is the cafeteria and the item shop. They also sell
grimoires, so if you need one, let's purchase it."

The healing magic that Liese uses can be learned from grimoires.
Grimoires can be purchased at shops like \N[262] and \N[265].

On the other hand, most of the attack magic is acquired as Liese levels
up.

Grimoires can also be purchased with \ii[141] and \ii[147], but please
note that Liese has already mastered \ns[56] and \ns[62].

Additionally, after learning magic, the grimoire will not disappear
but will remain in the 'Grimoires' section of the items menu.
